        <Summary>A powerful batch renamer for KDE</Summary>
        <Description>KRename is a powerful batch renamer for KDE. It allows you to easily rename hundreds or even thousand of files in one go. The filenames can be created by parts of the original filename, numbering the files or accessing hundreds of details about the file, like creation date, or the Exif information of an image.</Description>
